OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with one or two showers
OL,6,Fto start the day. The cloud soon
OL,7,Fclears to give a very warm, or hot day
OL,8,Ffor some, with plenty of sunny spells.
OL,9,FRemaining cooler along the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA settled night with light
OL,12,Fwinds and clear spells allowing mist
OL,13,Fand fog to form in places. Mild in
OL,14,Furban areas but cooler in rural spots.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FA hot day with some cloudy
OL,17,Fperiods during the morning followed by
OL,18,Fa bright and sunny afternoon. Cooler
OL,19,Falong the coast with a refreshing sea
OL,20,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
