OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FLargely bright and sunny throughout
OL,7,Fand notably hot on Monday.
OL,8,FTemperatures falling closer to average
OL,9,Fon Tuesday and Wednesday and becoming
OL,10,Fbreezy with varying amounts of cloud
OL,11,Fcover.
